title: Selected Sermons - Dr. Samuel C. Gipp
description:
Each volume in this series incorporates five sermons that Dr. Gipp has preached around the world.
Volume 2 contains: Elijah's Mistake; Seven Times Jesus Spoke After His Ascension; Tongues; Beyond Meat; and, Something's Gone Right.
Volume 3 contains: They've Stolen Your Love; What I've Learned About Men From the Bible; What I've About the Devil From the Bible; What I've Learned About God From the Bible; and, Don't Give It Back!


About the author:
Dr. Gipp is a former pastor, an evangelist, teacher, author and Bible conference speaker. He has the unique ability to digest large amounts of information and then present it in an analytical, understandable, format. His humerous, informative and forceful preaching style make him popular with all ages and keeps him in demand as a Revivalist and Bible conference speaker
